{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d070aeb7ab","title":"关于邀请刘澜涛参加中央讨论经济工作的会议的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4d248f3325","index":0,"year":1953,"month":5,"day":24,"articleId":"d070aeb7ab"}],"tags":[{"id":"3dcf7883ce","name":"刘澜涛","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"845477373d","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d070aeb7ab","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘澜涛，当时任中央人民政府国家计划委员会委员、华北行政委员会主席。尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"cdd7748ff6","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d070aeb7ab","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"d92adcf38d","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d070aeb7ab","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中央政治局会议准备讨论的两个议题：（一）第一机械工业部关于目前国营机械工业的情况及今后工作部署的指示（草稿）。（二）国家计划委员会主席高岗关于同意苏联方面三年建成长春汽车厂的建议给毛泽东并中央的报告。"}],"contents":[{"id":"aa649f188b","type":"title","text":"关于邀请刘澜涛参加中央过论经济工作的会议的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d070aeb7ab"},{"id":"845477373d","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆P同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d070aeb7ab"},{"id":"cdd7748ff6","type":"paragraph","text":"而后中央讨论经济工作（工业及其他）的时候，请邀刘澜涛同志到会，并将文件预发他看。星期一讨论高岗同志的两个议程以，请即照此办理。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d070aeb7ab"},{"id":"d92adcf38d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d070aeb7ab"},{"id":"db97e99571","type":"paragraph","text":"五月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"d070aeb7ab"}],"page":{"id":"